{"tid":581327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★自殺冇人理？男子疑由行車天橋墮下　掛屍山坡數天始被發現","createTime":"2018-03-05T09:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T10:09:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"58e080f47a6f9358d2780ca84c93a0fa70ac257a","tid":581327,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:01:35.000Z","msg":"近中午時分，一名釣魚客於西環大口環道31號對開石灘，驚見有男子掛於離地約3米的石牆上，懷疑已經死亡，大驚報警。警員、消防員及救護員趕到現場，由穿上保護衣物的消防員爬梯將男子帶回地面。現場人員證實男事主為一名老翁，已經明顯死亡，<span style=\"color: red;\">更已傳出屍臭，有蒼蠅圍繞，相信男子已死去數天</span>。警方仍封鎖現場調查，由於石灘對上20餘米為一條行車天橋，不排除老翁是由上址墮下身亡，不過老翁是意外失足還是自殺，仍有待警方調查。據了解，老翁年約七旬，為附近居民，早前出門晨運後就不知所終。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/165146/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%96%91%E7%94%B1%E8%A1%8C%E8%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B-%E6%8E%9B%E5%B1%8D%E5%B1%B1%E5%9D%A1%E6%95%B8%E5%A4%A9%E5%A7%8B%E8%A2%AB%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F165146%2F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%2594%25B1%25E8%25A1%258C%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25A9%258B%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E4%25B8%258B-%25E6%258E%259B%25E5%25B1%258D%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%259D%25A1%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25A7%258B%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE&d=mR%2Fc%2Bzps6cEDNrZ8EtMDxWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=83d10706\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/165146/%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%96%91%E7%94%B1%E8%A1%8C%E8%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E6%A9%8B%E5%A2%AE%E4%B8%8B-%E6%8E%9B%E5%B1%8D%E5%B1%B1%E5%9D%A1%E6%95%B8%E5%A4%A9%E5%A7%8B%E8%A2%AB%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE</a>"},{"pid":"f1b140688f19b005647354e20de0dd60ca60efba","tid":581327,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:02:23.000Z","msg":"自殺宣傳力=零"},{"pid":"0ba4f0509929c447d46f1f7f73e257caecf0c27c","tid":581327,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:06:47.000Z","msg":"支那01"},{"pid":"a1956d478012e09